  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_095_000142",
    "sentence": "朝野士庶，聞者鹹嘆惜之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_007_095_000143",
    "sentence": "翟璋，未詳何許人也。",
